## 🙌 Why This License?

EthervoxAI is built on principles of openness, privacy, and user control. This license ensures:

- Developers remain free to experiment and contribute.
- Users benefit from innovations without being tracked or monetized.
- Companies must collaborate ethically or negotiate commercial usage.

---

## 👥 Contributor Agreement

By contributing to EthervoxAI (code, design, documentation), you agree your contribution falls under this license and you have the legal right to offer it.

See [CONTRIBUTING.md](CONTRIBUTING.md) for contribution details.

---

## 💬 Questions?

Reach out to the maintainers via GitHub Issues or email:  
